comments.body:
@marcofleon since we use a latch for all threads of the pool, if more than one thread is executing an iteration at a time with the same pool it will deadlock.
So, I opted to not use the similar pattern we have for the threadpool fuzz harness.
Will this still work with your fuzzing infrastructure, or should I try a different approach with the latch?

